":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18564,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/17\/call-upon-allah-with-yaqin\/","url_meta":{"origin":34581,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Conviction: Call upon Allah with certainty, without distraction","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cCall upon Allah with certainty that He will answer you. Know that Allah will not answer the supplication of an unmindful and distracted heart.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3479 Grade: Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/29\/true-wealth-not-outward\/","url_meta":{"origin":34581,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hearts: True wealth is not outward, rather in the heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRichness does not exist outwardly. Verily, true richness is the richness of the soul. If Allah wills goodness for a servant, He places richness in his soul and righteousness in his heart. If Allah wills harm\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/